    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">How to Edit a 2D-Cam, Gear-Pair, or Profile?</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="VariableName">To edit a 2D-Cam, Gear-Pair, Profile, Extrusion.</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">There are certain elements that are coincident with each other in the graphic-area.</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">For example: A <text styleclass="Element">Polyline</text> element may be above a <text styleclass="Element">2D-Cam</text><text styleclass="Body Text">, and a</text>&#32;<text styleclass="Element">Profile/ Extrusion</text> element may be above the <text styleclass="Element">Polyline</text>.</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text">When you want to edit one of these elements - the &#160;- you may find you open a dialog-box that you do not want to open. </text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text">To edit the element that you want to edit </text><text styleclass="Element">2D-Cam, Polyline, Profile</text><text styleclass="Body Text">, or </text><text styleclass="Element">Extrusion</text></para>
    <para styleclass="VariableName-indent">There are two basic procedures:</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1" style="cell-padding:0px; border-width:0px; border-spacing:0px; cell-border-width:0px; border-style:none;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="VariableName">PROCEDURE 1 </text><text styleclass="T_Menu">- Selection-Window</text> (preferred)</para>
          <list id="4" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Numbered" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered"><text style="font-style:italic;">Click</text> the element<text style="font-style:normal;"> you want to edit</text> the graphic-area<text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="HowTo Numbered"><text styleclass="VariableName-indent">All</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> of the coincident elements will show in the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-ProjectExplorer-SelectionWindow" styleclass="Body Text">Selection-Window</link></para>
          <list id="5" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="2" styleclass="HowTo Numbered" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered"><text style="font-style:normal;">Right-click</text> the element you want to edit<text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered"><text style="font-style:normal;">Click</text>&#32;<text styleclass="VariableName">Edit Element</text> in the contextual-menu</li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="VariableName">PROCEDURE 2</text><text style="font-weight:bold;"> - </text><text styleclass="T_Menu">Assembly-Tree </text></para>
          <list id="6" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Numbered" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered">Find the element in the <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Assembly-Tree">Assembly-Tree</link><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
          </list>
          <list id="7" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="2" styleclass="HowTo Numbered" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered"><text style="font-style:normal;">Click</text><text style="font-style:italic;">&#32;</text><text style="font-style:normal;">the element in the Assembly</text>-<text style="font-weight:normal;">Tree to select it</text><text styleclass="VariableName">. </text></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered"><text style="font-style:normal;">Right-click</text> the element you want to edit<text style="font-weight:bold;">&#32;</text></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered"><text style="font-style:normal;">Click</text>&#32;<text styleclass="VariableName">Edit Element</text> in the contextual-menu</li>
          </list>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
